00071 typedef struct OLD_SM_Dep
00072 {
00073     unsigned char       type;           /* type of dependence arc */
00074     unsigned char       from_index;     /* index of src operand of dep arc */
00075     unsigned char       to_index;       /* index of dest operand of dep arc */
00076     short               omega;          /* dependence distance in iterations */
00077     short               distance;       /* dependence latency */
00078     struct OLD_SM_Oper  *from_op;       /* src operation of dep arc */

00080     struct OLD_SM_Dep   *from_next_dep; /* next output dep in src oper */
00081     struct OLD_SM_Dep   *to_next_dep;   /* next input dep in dest oper */
00082 } OLD_SM_Dep;
